'''Oqa membranes''' were tubes used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] to connect two ships in space, for transfer between them. They were the equivalent of [[Docking tube/Legends|cofferdams]] and were made from [[microbial mat]]s. Their name came from [[oqa]].

